(20, 'The End of a Bad Habit, New Website, and a Deep Message', 'Hello and welcome back to another yet exciting blog entry from the kid who makes epic dance music and the one who is an avid anime freak! He is now back from a loooong running time of taking a break from blogging and doing all things awesome in the world! Hi, I am Nat4an and this is my website (my place to be me). I writing this today, not to get out to the world but to be an entry that I can use for my own personal benefit.<br /><br />[!--more--]\r\nYou see for the longest time, all my life, I have been plagued with a curse of biting my finger nails. I know it is one of the hardest habits to quit. But that is all going to change. I bought a 3-week pack of a substance called Omega-3 Control-It stuff and I plan to use it to rid my habit for good and I am now blogging about my journey starting now.<br /><br />\r\nToday would officially mark Day 2 of Operation Stop-Biting-Your-Nails. Along with that, I have been making some headway on the new website. I would like to point out that I work a full time job so it is hard to write every single day. But when I do, they are good. Good is a word that we often say just to get people to stop talking. Talking is what we do on a normal day-to-day routine. Routines are something that we make to create new things for ourselves. Ourselves are prideful things that need attention (love and care). Love and care is something plenty of us get but far often do we often go about forgetting about something to love and care on? Wow. This blog entry has turned into something that became deep. I like deep things. Like a puddle of mud or water that a Rubicon Jeep slides through.<br /><br />\r\nWhat do you think you could do to make someone''s day?<br /><br />\r\nHow much have you done today?<br /><br />\r\nDid you enjoy today?<br /><br />\r\nThat is all, thanks for reading and I am glad you came to read this. God bless!<br />\r\nNat4an', 1, 1, 'new website,omega,biting nails,habit,bad things,deep message,people,', '2012-08-03 14:49:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 2012, '08', '03', '14', '49', '24', 'yes', 'Published', 'no', ''),
