(24, 'restrict all', 'bio', 'double', 'Biography', 'the musik maker,bio,', 'pad3', 4, '', '2012-09-19', '', 'echo "<h2 class=\\"pages-maincontent-title\\">The Bio of Nat4an as The Musik Maker</h2>";\r\n	echo "<div class=\\"pages-maincontent-content\\">";\r\n	echo "<h3>DJ Trancecoder (born Jun 2012)</h3><p>Born out the beautiful state of Texas, DJ Trancecoder wishes that he grew up in the UK so that he could have been use to mixing trance like the pros. </p>\r\n	\r\n	<p>DJ Trancecoder started listening to trance when he was around the age of 16 but didn''''t start mixing it until around late 2011. I know, I know. He was born in the month of June (year of 2012) and started mixing trance in 2011? The truth behind this is that DJ Trancecoder learned to mix in 2011 but didn''''t start making it big until June 2011. Glad I could clear that up for you.</p>\r\n	\r\n	<p>I mix all types of trance: Progressive (my favorite), Hard Trance, and even a bit of Uplifting Trance. I may not be as good as the next biggest Trance Sensation but I am learning and my heart is in the right place.</p>\r\n	\r\n	<p>I believe that if you set yourself aside from the popularity and the struggle that it takes to mix good trance (become one with your music) then it is a humbling experience and everyone else thinks better of you.</p>\r\n	<p>Main Program: FL Studio 10<br />Type: DAW</p>\r\n	\r\n	<p>VSTs: Sylenth, Tone2 Warmverb, Nexus 2, Gladiator, and others</p>\r\n	\r\n	<p>Soundpacks: All Vengence Essential Collection Series</p>\r\n	\r\n	<p>Enjoy the mixes I have because they are one in a million and there are more coming!</p>";\r\n	echo "</ul>";\r\necho "</div>";', '', '', '$GET_MODULES=mysql_query("SELECT * FROM {$properties->DB_PREFIX}pages_modules WHERE page=''$page'' AND sidebar=''1'' AND launchpad=''$launchpadPN'' ORDER BY arr") or die(''uh oh! ''.mysql_error());\r\nwhile($FETCH_MODULES=mysql_fetch_array($GET_MODULES)){\r\n	$title=$FETCH_MODULES[''title''];\r\n	$contents=$FETCH_MODULES[''contents''];\r\n	$toggle_title=$FETCH_MODULES[''toggle_title''];\r\n	$toggle_visible=$FETCH_MODULES[''toggle_visible''];\r\n	if($toggle_title == "off"){/* no title */} else if($toggle_title == "on"){echo "<h2 class=\\"pages-sidebar-title\\">{$title}</h2>";}\r\n	echo "<div class=\\"pages-sidebar-contents\\">";\r\n		//convert contents\r\n		$contents=converter($properties,$contents,''basic'',''to'');\r\n		if($toggle_visible == "on"){eval($contents);}else if($toggle_visible == "off"){/* not visible */}\r\n	echo "</div>";\r\n}', '', '', '', '', 'no', 'off', 'Published', 0, ''),
