(2, 'Do you have a playlist of anime songs that I can listen to?', 'Woah! Such a specific question! Of course I do! When you are ready, click here to check it out!', 'yes'),
(3, 'I want some anime that has sexy girls in it, do you have any recommendations', 'Ha. That''s 99.635% of anime. Oh your serious? Well for starters you could try out Rosario + Vampire, Highschool of the Dead, Shuffle!, and Demon King Daimao. That should be enough for a starter kit for ya.', 'yes'),
(4, 'Sub''d or Dub''d', 'That is such a controversial topic in the world of true anime. It depends. If you have seen an anime in Sub''d (english) first then don''t watch an anime in Dub''d (english) because it won''t sound right. If you have only seen an anime in Dub''d (english) then it isn''t as bad. But I have to say: seeing anime in Sub''d (english) sometimes is refreshing because you get to hear what the actual voices sound like but you have to think more due to the fact that you have to interpret what the sub is saying and watch the scene but hey do what ever you like.', 'yes'),
(5, 'What anime are you interested in', 'Cute, Cosplay-type, Hentai (nah''jk but everyone should like this - in a good way.), Action-oriented, Romantic, Sad (ones that will leave me in a depressive-state from not watching them when they are over), Sci-fi, Magical, and those that I can''t describe which means the rest! ^_^', 'yes'),
(6, 'What anime do you recommend for me for action/violence', 'Death Note, Chrome Shelled Regios, Highschool of The Dead, Aquarion, Kaze no Stigma, and that enough for starters.', 'yes'),
(7, 'What was the first anime that you actually cried on', ' All of them. I mean Clannad (and Clannad After Story), Blue Drop (I almost shed a tear)', 'yes'),
(8, 'What was the first anime you ever saw', 'Highschool of the Dead (and I LOVED it!!!)', 'yes'),
(9, 'When did you get into anime', 'I was "into" anime just like everyone was: around junior high and high school but I wasn''t officially into anime until the year 2011 when I became OBSESSED after getting a new job and having money to spend on an actual Netflix Subscription!!!', 'yes'),
(10, 'Where do you watch your anime', 'On Netflix mostly. If I can''t find a certain anime I want to watch I will go to places like 2anime or I go here for all my anime!', 'yes');
